Ludh Harun


1  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Musa niya, 
2  “Nyis jo-Israel mondo jotend dhoot ka dhoot omiyi luth achiel achiel, duto ludhe apar gariyo, ma moro ka moro ondikie nying jatelo ka jatelo. 
3  Kuom ludh dhood Lawi to mondo indikie nying Harun, nimar luth ka luth nyaka bed mar jatelo ka jatelo. 
4  Eka iketgi duto e Hema e nyim Sandug Rapar, kama aromoe kodu, 
5  kendo ng’at ma ludhe oloth e ng’at ma ayiero. Mano e kaka abiro tieko ng’ur ma jo-Israel ng’urnigo.”


6  Kuom mano, Musa nowuoyo gi jo-Israel mi jatend dhoot ka dhoot nomiye luth, duto ludhe apar gariyo, koriwore gi mar Harun. 
7  Musa noketogi e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye ei Hemb Rapar. 
8  

Kinyne ka ne odonjo e Hema, noyudo ka ludh Harun, ma ludh dhood Lawi, ema oloth. Adier, noloth mogolo ite kod thiepe, kendo onyago olembe! 
9  Eka Musa nogolo ludhego oko, monyiso jo-Israel duto. Ne ginenogi gi wang’gi, kendo jatelo ka jatelo nokawo mare. 
10  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Musa niya, “Dwok ludh Harun e nyim Sandug Rapar, obed ranyisi ma siemo joma wigi tek duto, mondo owe ywakna chuth, eka ok ginitho.” 
11  Musa notimo mana kaka Ruoth Nyasaye nochike.


12  Bang’e jo-Israel nowacho ni Musa niya, “Waserwenyo! Waduto warumo! 
13  Ng’ato ang’ata kuomwa mosudo machiegni gi Hema Maler mar Nyasaye biro tho! Wabiro tho waduto koso?”

